-id=\"39ae7870dac2b7f1d3e71288fb1ec7f43a637f98\"> <img src=\"http://media.guim.co.uk/39ae7870dac2b7f1d3e71288fb1ec7f43a637f98/0_0_326_499/326.jpg\" alt=\"The bolds Julian Clary cover\" width=\"326\" height=\"499\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\"></span> </figcaption> </figure>  <p>There are lots of sad, happy and puzzling moments in this book.</p> <p>I liked this book because the illustrations were fabulous, the plot was interesting and funny, the descriptions were good and I could not put the book down, wanting to find out what happens next. </p> <p>I would recommend this book to bookworms who love jokes.</p> <aside class=\"element element-rich-link element--thumbnail\"> <p> <span>Related: </span><a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/childrens-books/2011/mar/02/how-do-i-get-involved-guardian-childrens-books\">How do I get involved in the Guardian children's books site?</a> </p> </aside>  <ul> <li><strong>Buy this book at the <a href=\"https://bookshop.theguardian.com/catalog/product/view/id/317819/\">Guardian Bookshop</a></strong></li> </ul> <h2><strong>Want to tell the world about a book you’ve read? <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/books/childrens-books/2011/mar/02/how-do-i-get-involved-guardian-childrens-books\">Join the site</a> and send us your review!</strong></h2>","liveBloggingNow":"false","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/4gah8","wordcount":"225","standfirst":"<p>‘I would recommend this book to bookworms who love jokes’</p>"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2016/feb/12/the-bolds-julian-clary-review","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/2016/feb/12/the-bolds-julian-clary-review","sectionName":"Children's books","elements":[{"id":"39ae7870dac2b7f1d3e71288fb1ec7f43a637f98","relation":"body","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","file":"http://media.guim.co.uk/39ae7870dac2b7f1d3e71288fb1ec7f43a637f98/0_0_326_499/326.jpg","typeData":{"role":"thumbnail","mediaApiU